modName: Honey Fingers Male redguard save-racemenu preset
summary: Save game/racemenu preset of a male Redguard character.
descriptionHtml:
Please forgive my english, not my first language. Please forgive my terrible graphics, I'm on a toaster. I did the best I can.

As I like to call him, "Honey-Fingers" [i](yeah, I know it's a lame name, don't worry)[/i] is a Redguard character I made recently and would like to share. He's almost default (very generic as well) but I think if you want something a bit different than the vanilla presets to work on and customize I think it's good start. I don't really understand the first thing about modding but I thought someone may be interested in a male Redguard preset so I decided to share.

There's the save version created using "coc whiterun" command and the racemenu present.  About his neck, I don't know how to fix it, I just put on a necklace. You are absolutely free to do whatever you want with the preset/save game no need to ask permission or anything.

Here's the mods that you will need for him to look like in the screenshot):
- [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/4141/]High Res Face Maps for Men by Geonox (smooth version)[/url]﻿
- [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722]The Eyes of Beauty[/url]﻿
- [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/29624]RaceMenu (if you are going to use the present)[/url]﻿
- SKSE

Some extra stuff:
- [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/90/]Hairier male texture (body texture I'm using)[/url]
- [url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2094/]Barbarian Thief (armor he's using)[/url]
author: larcenyinthablood
